subject: Hello dear,
body:
Hello dear,
I am pleased to inform you that a concrete arrangement has been made for
your long-delayed fund to be released any moment from now.
I hope you respond promptly for more details.
Warm regards.
Regards,
Ikuku Idoko.

subject: Re:   Hello dear,
body:
Hello Ikuku Idoko,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm glad to hear that the concrete has been made for my fund to be released soon. Could you please provide me with more details about the process? I want to make sure I understand everything correctly.

Looking forward to your response.

Best wishes,
Alonzo
